<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038084" n="1"/>
  <opener><lb/><del><gap/></del><salute>
      <lb/>Viro Reverend<del><gap/></del><add>o</add> et Clarissimo
      <lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> Abbati <rs type="person">Fardell<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs></salute>
    <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr></opener>
<p><lb/>Intellexi ex ultimis Illustris Domini <rs type="person">Leibnitii</rs> ad <rs type="person">Patruum</rs> meum
  <lb/><rs type="letter">literis</rs>, <del><gap/></del><add>T</add>e non minimam <del><gap/></del>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endationibus Tuis apud <rs type="person">Proceres
    <lb/>Venetos</rs> dare operam, ut cathedra Mathematica in <rs type="organisation">Lyceo Patavino</rs> per
  <lb/>discessum <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Hermanni</rs> nostri vacua relicta mihi demandetur, pro quo fa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vore et insigni officio dignas ago gratias rogans ut eandem in me benevo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lentiam continuare et ulterioribus <del><gap/></del>co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endationibus apud <rs type="person">Amicos</rs>, si id
  <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> re esse <del><gap/></del>videbitur, in<del><gap/></del><add>stare</add> digneris. Significavit <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Leibnitius</rs>, forte
  <lb/>juventutem meam mihi impedimento fore, eaque de causa suasit <rs type="person">Patruo</rs> meo
  <lb/>ut ipse sibi aucto stipendio spartam hanc <del><gap/></del>conferri pateretur, verum <del><gap/></del>ipsi
  <lb/>res su<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> non permittunt ut sedem et familiam alio transferat, quod<del><gap/></del>
  <lb/><del></del><add>simulque</add> ut plurima Tibi dicta salute significem
  <lb/><add><choice><sic>maximus</sic><corr>maximas</corr></choice> pro propensa <unclear reason="illegible">T</unclear>ua in nos voluntate gratias agam<del><gap/></del></add>
  <lb/>in mandatis mihi dedit <rs type="person">Patruus</rs>. Ego quidem qui delectationis
  <lb/>duntaxat gratia operam dedi <add>studio</add> Mathe<del></del><add>matico</add> nunquam ad hanc cathedr<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
  <lb/>aspirassem, nisi me inscium co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endassent atque post<del></del><add>ea</add> incitassent
  <lb/>amici et Patroni D. <rs type="person">Leibnitius</rs>, <rs type="person">Hermannus</rs>, <rs type="person">Varignon</rs> et <rs type="person">Patruus</rs>,
  <lb/>qui <add>me</add> non sine fructu <del></del><add>Mathematicas disciplinas</add> in Academiis docere posse<del></del>
  <lb/><del></del><add>arbitrati sunt</add>, quorum <del></del>hortationibus obediendum esse duxi,
  <lb/>Gratum igitur facies si porro hoc negotium co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>endatione Tua juvabis,
  <lb/>ego nihil intermittam quo gratus in Te animus aut officia mea,
  <lb/>si qua forte Tibi usui esse poterunt, constare <del></del><add>queant</add>. </p>
<closer><salute>Vale et fave<supplied>.</supplied></salute>
  <lb/><dateline><date when="1713-08-31">31. <abbr>Aug.</abbr> 1713</date>.</dateline></closer>
</div>
</body>
